1. The subjects have moderate-to-severe volume loss in the cheeks.
2. The subjects were randomized in a split-face design.
3. The subjects underwent malar enhancement.
4. Cohesive Polydensified Matrix 26 mg/ml HA (CPM-26) was used for malar enhancement.
5. Vycross 20 mg/ml HA (VYC-20) was also used for malar enhancement.
6. Both CPM-26 and VYC-20 were used on different halves of the face.
